{"tid":2269293,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"警方正式起訴浸大編委記者阻差辦公及拒捕","createTime":"2020-11-03T11:36:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-03T11:48:58.000Z","uid":240362,"like":5,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"656c16ab9130e3d1cedb35dbd5a26333bd5b4d59","tid":2269293,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T11:36:37.000Z","msg":"加山傳播 DB Channel:<br />\n<br />\n今年5月9號有網民號召在中環發起「和你Lunch」，其中浸大編委記者鄧澤旻被警員包圍後拘捕。案件擾攘多時，日前警方要求鄧今日再報到，並剛剛正式被律政司起訴他「妨礙公職人員執行職務」罪及拒捕罪。<br />\n<br />\n鄧澤旻於5月9號採訪網民號召在中環發起的「和你Lunch」期間，被警方指他干犯公眾地方行為不檢及拒捕，之後更以暴力對待鄧並拉到暗處，及後押回中區警署。<br />\n<br />\n案件事隔接近半年，鄧澤旻上月28號再到警署報到時，案件主管對鄧表示將原定今月5號再報到的時間提早至昨日，並表明為「最後一次」，即抑或撤案，或是正式落案起訴，但昨日臨到報到時間時，又再押後至今日。鄧進入警署時已表示自己很有可能被落案起訴，坦言對警方打壓傳媒行為不樂觀。<br />\n<br />\n文/N<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/109301110486297/posts/368843444532061/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F109301110486297%2Fposts%2F368843444532061%2F&d=AZYGjn5ll7vy7cK20AVbo6nyrFheAedOz%2Bkyyi3ikZI%3D&h=83a813bc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/109301110486297/posts/368843444532061/</a>"},{"pid":"758f88fca6dfc0a6e9627b24772090fe05dbc34d","tid":2269293,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T11:37:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d97f72cc3ce47e645982f2ece20b87a4bcfffb99","tid":2269293,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"758f88fca6dfc0a6e9627b24772090fe05dbc34d","tid":2269293,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T11:37:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-1